                            </additions>
                            <decoDesc>
                                <p>Main text in brown-black ink. Rubrics and some underlining in red. Capitals touched in yellow <locus from="1v" to="2v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="36v" to="36v" scheme="folios"/>, and in red <locus from="5r" to="9r" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="38r" to="38r" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="71r" to="72r" scheme="folios"/>. Green ink added to plain initial in red <locus from="115v" to="115v" scheme="folios"/>.</p>
                                <p>Three drawings in the margins, see further under Additions.</p>
                                <decoNote type="initials">
                                    <p> Five larger initials. <locus from="1r" to="1r" scheme="folios"/>: Decorated initial <quote>Q</quote> over 6 lines. Black background with reserved space for the letter and the leaf-shaped decorations in the counterspace, both outlined and further decorated in red; <locus from="68v" to="68v" scheme="folios"/>: Decorated initial <quote>V</quote> over 10 lines, outlined in red and partially filled with red and blue. Leaf-shaped decorations outlined in red in the counterspace, the background in goldlike yellow; <locus from="84v" to="84v" scheme="folios"/>: Decorated initial <quote>O</quote> over 8 lines, with flourishes in purple-pink extending above and below. The letter is outlined in red, with leaf-shaped decorations in the counterspace, the background in goldlike yellow; <locus from="103v" to="103v" scheme="folios"/>: Initial <quote>D</quote> over 6 lines, with flourishes in purple-pink. The letter is outlined in red, with leaf-shaped decorations
                                        in the counterspace, the background in goldlike yellow; <locus from="131r" to="131r" scheme="folios"/>: Plain initial <quote>P</quote> over 10 lines in black ink with pen-flourishes in the counter space and around the outline, the latter washed with red.</p>
                                    <p>
